Package Model

Class YearView

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.YearView
  • public class YearView
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the number of appointments by month for a specific characteristic.

    Use for tables using a yearly view.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    David Vaca
